content: Doesn't remind and now it can't open quote

Im a huge fan of Gabby but I have to echo many of the reviewers of the past year plus in complaining about the 'reminders' not working. I don't get notifications or reminders until I open the app itself. As a healthcare provider in a crazy covid world I would love a daily reminder to stop for a moment, read the affirmation and center myself...sad that this app can't help me with that. This has clearly been an issue for awhile now; I think it's time for an update!!!
I was expecting audio affirmation. I find this app useless.

Disappointing! I was so excited to get this app, but the only thing that works is the daily affirmation. Sorry, but much as I love Gabby Bernstein, it really isn't worth the cost. I've uninstalled and refunded. Hopefully it will improve in the future and I'll try again
Lovely affirmations but the push notifications dont work. Could you fix it please?
Thanks you Gabby!! ‚ù§üôè

I love this app, it's exactly what I was looking for. Simple affirmations that resonate (like everything I've read by Gabby B üíó), beautiful backgrounds, daily reminder notifications, plus I can export to Photos and save as my wallpaper so every time I check my phone I do my daily affirmation. Love love love. 4 stars instead of 5 because the notification doesn't always make a sound when it's supposed to, sometimes it will ring instead when I turn on the screen.

Push notifications don't work. I love the app itself, but the push notifications stopped working. It's a little frustrating since I paid for it. I have free apps that works better. I just hope it gets fixed soon.
This app is basic and not worth paying for. Plus it hasn't been updated in over a year. This is just a money grab. Disappointed.

So disappointing to pay and download, and the only thing that works is the daily affirmation. Reminders don't work. It seems I'm not the only one. Ease do more testing before releasing. Sadly uninstalled and refunded :(
disappointed. downloaded the app and shows only the affirmation of the day, no access to anything else. also the timer did not work.

I love the daily affirmations. I just wish the rest of the app worked correctly. With the daily reminder turned on, I either get 2 notifications a day, or none. When attempting to see past affirmations, the app just goes back to the daily affirmation. I expect this app to work properly considering its a paid app. The app had just restructured it when I purchased, Very disappointed.
paid for an app that doesnt do what its supposed too. never notifies me. want a refund.
waste of money when similar free content available on Facebook. i thought this would be more guided meditation, rather than just random positive thoughts.
The reminders do not work. This is very frustrating because the app wasn't free.Great content but if you miss the days message, there's no way to view themüò®ü§î
again the reminders are not working

I am a big fan of all things Gabby. And I love the idea of this app. However I am unable to set reminders even though I have uninstalled and reinstalled it twice. Also finding the same affirmation repeating itself entirely sooner than I would anticipate.
Motivational, easy to use and customize alerts. Hopefully, backgrounds and more customization feature will be added soon.
If it has Gabrielle Bernstein's name on it, 5 stars is to low. I give her 10 starsüåüüåüüåüüåüüåü üåüüåüüåüüåüüåü and 5 ‚ù§‚ù§‚ù§‚ù§‚ù§ red hearts!
The problem with the app is that the reminder doesn't work...please make an alarm that works with airplane mode (as the majority of alarm apps) thanks
I really like Gabby's books and writing but I am finding most of these affirmations sort of basic, not really deep, too out of context. Love the idea, just not working for me.

Please create a silent daily reminder/repeat affirmation option (more like a notification and less like an alarm). It would be great if I could program a repeat notification to pop up throughout the day that doesn't ring like an alarm, but just flashes on the screen. This way I could use the app at work and at other times when I need my phone to be silent. Also, it would be better if the affirmation appears right away, rather than having to click on the menu option to display today's affirmation. Thank you!
Love it! Simple and beautiful and very helpful
My affirmations have been the same now for 3 days. Every time I click on today's affirmations or reminders it just keeps going back to the same screen üò¢
I love Gabby, but this is not worth the $2. It's so plain and basic and I am genuinely disappointed. I'll keep using her 52 card deck instead.
Love the affirmations

Oh my gosh! I have been waiting for years for a Spirit Junkie app for Android. It is great and lots more than I would have expected. You can set reminders to start your day with a great selection of sounds. A reminder at 11:11 comes pre-loaded. You can also select favorite affirmations from a pre-loaded history. Loving it. Thanks, Gabby and app team.
